title: Married2Med: Barns & Ignoble
description:
The "Married To Medicine" tour of Savannah continues with a semi-masked dinner in a barn. Along the way, Quad makes a dramatic speech, Mariah endorses "Game of Thrones," and Contessa hoards some leftovers. Good times had by all!
Get tix to our live shows: http://watchwhatcrappens.com
